WEBVTT

00:00.024 --> 00:04.972
♪ Hey, why is it happening ♪

00:05.944 --> 00:08.652
♪ My heart is racing ♪

00:09.784 --> 00:13.792
♪ The world has fallen silent ♪

00:13.816 --> 00:18.572
♪ Hey, when I imagine you ♪

00:19.608 --> 00:22.636
♪ What kind of look ♪

00:23.640 --> 00:27.584
♪ Attracted me to you ♪

00:27.608 --> 00:30.880
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:30.904 --> 00:34.368
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

00:34.392 --> 00:39.640
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

00:39.640 --> 00:41.258
♪ I love you ♪

00:41.258 --> 00:44.736
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:44.760 --> 00:48.032
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

00:48.056 --> 00:53.728
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

00:53.752 --> 00:55.096
♪ I love you ♪

00:55.096 --> 00:58.432
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:58.456 --> 01:01.804
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

01:01.912 --> 01:07.109
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

01:07.109 --> 01:08.792
♪ I love you ♪

01:08.792 --> 01:12.192
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

01:12.216 --> 01:15.616
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

01:15.640 --> 01:21.216
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

01:21.240 --> 01:24.652
♪ I love you ♪

01:26.930 --> 01:27.720
=Love Me, Love My Voice=

01:27.720 --> 01:30.568
=Love Me, Love My Voice=
=Episode 2=

01:30.568 --> 01:33.760
(Shengshengman, I love you.)

01:34.920 --> 01:38.119
Our business partners are there too.

01:38.119 --> 01:41.459
And the music director, Shengshengman.

01:42.399 --> 01:45.500
Come on, stop hesitating. Help me out.

01:46.039 --> 01:48.459
Say something. Anything.

01:49.892 --> 01:51.548
(Juemei Shayi, Online, Interactions)

01:56.480 --> 01:57.820
Shengshengman.

02:06.399 --> 02:08.019
Go on.

02:09.399 --> 02:11.040
Shengshengman.

02:11.040 --> 02:12.420
Sheng.

02:18.200 --> 02:19.548
Yeah.

02:20.160 --> 02:21.380
I'm here.

02:22.920 --> 02:24.700
Can you work with me?

02:32.999 --> 02:34.820
No problem.

02:37.399 --> 02:40.580
Qiang Qingci is showing us how to act.

02:44.800 --> 02:46.499
How does it work?

02:48.640 --> 02:50.519
Do you have any scripts at hand?

02:50.519 --> 02:53.039
(Perfect Voice Studio Internal Training)
Or is there a topic?

02:53.640 --> 02:56.320
(Welcome to the Internal Training)
There is a bulletin board here.

02:56.320 --> 02:59.820
The chat room admin
will post the lines here.

03:00.760 --> 03:02.439
I don't see it.

03:02.439 --> 03:03.279
They're preparing.

03:03.279 --> 03:04.619
It will be there.

03:07.040 --> 03:08.179
What's wrong?

03:12.760 --> 03:14.279
We can't upload the lines.

03:14.279 --> 03:15.719
Sheng, just a second.

03:15.719 --> 03:17.040
There's a problem.

03:17.040 --> 03:18.140
Okay.

03:19.600 --> 03:21.439
What do I do? I hope it's simple.

03:21.439 --> 03:24.380
It's okay. Don't worry. You got this.

03:28.160 --> 03:30.279
Just say something.

03:30.279 --> 03:32.880
Something simple.
Make sure everyone gets it.

03:32.880 --> 03:34.499
Come on, we're waiting.

03:41.959 --> 03:44.059
It's easy to show affection.

03:47.439 --> 03:48.660
Shengshengman.

03:54.040 --> 03:55.219
I love you.

04:04.239 --> 04:07.619
Do you love me?

04:23.840 --> 04:24.900
Yes, I do.

04:28.079 --> 04:31.699
I love your voice.

04:40.360 --> 04:42.900
Thank you. That's it.

04:44.400 --> 04:47.480
Love scenes are not
as complicated as you think.

04:47.480 --> 04:50.179
You don't have to be experienced.

04:51.280 --> 04:53.360
The key is to make the audience

04:53.360 --> 04:57.360
feel the sincerity in your lines.

04:57.360 --> 05:00.400
Dig deep. Know yourselves.

05:00.400 --> 05:03.559
Keep practicing. That's it.

05:03.559 --> 05:06.119
Amazing. That was awesome.

05:06.119 --> 05:08.020
It sounded real.

05:10.400 --> 05:12.619
He's a professional dubbing actor.

05:13.119 --> 05:14.679
Of course, he sounds real.

05:14.679 --> 05:16.439
He's said that line many times.

05:16.439 --> 05:18.259
I'll show you next time.

05:22.239 --> 05:24.800
I really admire his acting partners.

05:24.800 --> 05:27.480
How did they handle the confession?

05:27.480 --> 05:30.340
Didn't they fall in love with him?

05:32.040 --> 05:32.960
No idea.

05:32.960 --> 05:34.679
Isn't there any gossip about him?

05:34.679 --> 05:36.420
He never dated anyone from work?

05:36.960 --> 05:37.720
No idea.

05:37.720 --> 05:40.540
You know better. Think harder.

05:44.480 --> 05:48.780
I think there were some rumors.

05:49.960 --> 05:52.040
That was nice. It sounded even better

05:52.040 --> 05:53.436
than in those shows.

05:53.999 --> 05:57.720
Do you hear the booming sound

05:57.720 --> 05:58.879
of your racing heart?

05:58.879 --> 06:01.020
How many times
have you said "I love you" in shows?

06:02.480 --> 06:05.220
I don't remember,
but surely not as many as you.

06:06.840 --> 06:09.540
Dig deep. Keep practicing.

06:10.679 --> 06:11.780
Fine.

06:12.600 --> 06:17.420
Come on, guys.
Let's dig deep and keep practicing.

06:20.524 --> 06:22.684
(Girl's Dorm Building No. 3)

06:25.920 --> 06:27.220
(Shengshengman.)

06:29.040 --> 06:30.179
(I love you.)

06:32.639 --> 06:33.819
(Do you)

06:35.759 --> 06:37.100
(love me?)

06:38.759 --> 06:42.059
I'm back. I brought you some oden.

06:44.559 --> 06:45.800
She's asleep?

06:45.800 --> 06:47.199
So early?

06:47.199 --> 06:48.988
I got some for her too.

06:49.520 --> 06:50.759
You know what?

06:50.759 --> 06:57.439
Qiang Qingci said "I love you" to her.

06:57.439 --> 06:58.600
Really? When?

06:58.600 --> 06:59.720
Really.

06:59.720 --> 07:02.499
It was a line from the rehearsal.

07:03.239 --> 07:05.600
You scared me.

07:05.600 --> 07:08.720
It's still the first time
someone says that to you.

07:08.720 --> 07:09.600
Am I right?

07:09.600 --> 07:12.720
Yeah, why can't I get so lucky?

07:12.720 --> 07:14.679
He hasn't worked with someone for years.

07:14.679 --> 07:16.280
Sheng, you were lucky.

07:16.280 --> 07:19.199
He was the first guy who confessed to you.
You were so lucky.

07:19.199 --> 07:21.160
Stop making fun of me
if you want to copy my notes.

07:21.160 --> 07:23.480
Please, we're all counting on you.

07:23.480 --> 07:25.860
I bought you some snacks. Please enjoy.

07:27.160 --> 07:28.759
No, thanks. I've brushed my teeth.

07:28.759 --> 07:30.720
I'm going to bed. You should sleep too.

07:30.720 --> 07:33.379
The tests are starting tomorrow.

07:33.879 --> 07:35.059
Goodnight.

07:39.840 --> 07:43.619
- I hope...
- You can fall asleep.

07:44.920 --> 07:46.319
You...

07:46.319 --> 07:47.840
We're just jealous.

07:47.840 --> 07:49.800
Yeah, so jealous.

07:49.800 --> 07:51.379
I'm going to sleep.

07:53.199 --> 07:54.239
Sweet dreams.

07:54.239 --> 07:55.900
Dreaming about someone.

07:56.759 --> 07:58.140
Let's go.

08:04.360 --> 08:06.280
Oh, you mentioned the gossip

08:06.280 --> 08:08.499
about Qiang Qingci yesterday.

08:10.720 --> 08:11.920
Is there someone

08:11.920 --> 08:15.340
widely seen as his official couple?

08:16.920 --> 08:18.100
- No.
- No.

08:19.520 --> 08:21.756
Why not? Nobody brought it up?

08:23.240 --> 08:24.599
He introduced himself briefly

08:24.599 --> 08:27.500
when he first joined the studio.

08:31.559 --> 08:33.420
- I'm Qiang Qingci.
- (I'm Qiang Qingci.)

08:34.520 --> 08:35.932
- I'm single.
- (I'm single.)

08:36.439 --> 08:38.719
- I'll inform you once I get a girlfriend.
- (I'll inform you once I get a girlfriend.)

08:38.719 --> 08:42.000
So serious.
No one dared to make fun of him.

08:42.000 --> 08:44.760
And his fans are the toughest.

08:44.760 --> 08:46.040
Better not offend them.

08:46.040 --> 08:47.324
Yeah.

08:47.839 --> 08:48.920
So scary?

08:48.920 --> 08:51.040
Dig in. We have tests later.

08:51.040 --> 08:52.979
Yeah, right.

09:02.079 --> 09:04.880
Kids, the test will start soon.

09:04.880 --> 09:07.068
Turn off or mute your phones.

09:07.640 --> 09:08.959
I'm giving out papers.

09:08.959 --> 09:12.280
Write down your names,
classes, and class numbers first.

09:12.280 --> 09:13.740
Don't forget any.

09:13.740 --> 09:14.439
(Name: Gu Sheng)

09:14.439 --> 09:16.559
Stay quiet during the test.

09:16.559 --> 09:17.559
No conversing.

09:17.559 --> 09:19.620
Raise your hands if you need something.

09:29.160 --> 09:31.199
(The final tests
that last for two weeks)

09:31.199 --> 09:33.479
(mark the end
of the undergraduate years.)

09:33.479 --> 09:35.120
(They got the Perfect Voice Studio)

09:35.120 --> 09:38.540
(and Qiang Qingci
off my mind for a while.)

09:43.820 --> 09:46.428
(The Perfect Voice Studio)

09:59.040 --> 10:01.660
Get up. Time for breakfast.

10:05.599 --> 10:06.959
Coming.

10:06.959 --> 10:08.719
Zhou Zheng, hurry up.

10:08.719 --> 10:09.400
Morning.

10:09.400 --> 10:10.040
Morning.

10:10.040 --> 10:13.000
I bought the spring rolls you liked.

10:13.000 --> 10:14.839
Thanks. Hurry up, Zhou Zheng.

10:14.839 --> 10:16.900
Thank you.

10:22.199 --> 10:24.240
The same food?

10:24.240 --> 10:27.000
You said they were tasty.

10:27.000 --> 10:30.479
How's it going with that charity app?

10:30.479 --> 10:32.059
Which app?

10:36.240 --> 10:39.420
The one with Shengshengman?

10:44.079 --> 10:44.880
I spoke to them.

10:44.880 --> 10:46.719
They're having tests for two weeks.

10:46.719 --> 10:48.199
I said that was more important

10:48.199 --> 10:50.012
and we'd talk after that.

10:50.520 --> 10:52.319
Alright, let's wait.

10:52.319 --> 10:53.939
We're not in a rush.

10:59.719 --> 11:03.719
My bed. My goose. Did you miss me?

11:03.719 --> 11:07.620
Fourteen days of torment.
That's the end of the semester.

11:09.719 --> 11:11.719
Let's celebrate. I'm leaving tomorrow.

11:11.719 --> 11:13.439
Alright, no problem.

11:13.439 --> 11:14.640
What are we having tonight?

11:14.640 --> 11:17.280
I'll book a place for a barbecue?

11:17.280 --> 11:18.579
Alright.

11:19.959 --> 11:21.400
I have so many parcels to get.

11:21.400 --> 11:22.312
Let me get them.

11:22.312 --> 11:23.359
Need a hand?

11:23.359 --> 11:24.740
No, thanks.

11:26.359 --> 11:28.219
Let me check on my Weibo.

11:29.719 --> 11:31.160
You still remember that?

11:31.160 --> 11:32.988
Your 200 fans, do you still have them?

11:33.544 --> 11:36.679
(Login: Shengshengman)
At least, none of them is a robot.

11:36.679 --> 11:38.040
I've known many of them.

11:38.040 --> 11:40.459
They've been following me for two years.

11:42.559 --> 11:45.599
Our club leader told me
to verify my account after the tests.

11:45.599 --> 11:47.719
It's more formal. I'll need your help.

11:47.719 --> 11:48.939
I'm new to this.

11:57.559 --> 11:59.859
Why do I have so many new fans?

12:03.400 --> 12:04.439
Really.

12:04.439 --> 12:06.500
(Shengshengman 2999 Fans 351 Follow)
2999.

12:07.359 --> 12:08.956
Did you upload a new song?

12:09.479 --> 12:10.740
Not really.

12:11.599 --> 12:12.719
(All Fans)
Check them out.

12:12.719 --> 12:14.492
(Perfect Voice_Qiang Qingci)

12:18.240 --> 12:20.520
Qiang Qingci is following you, Sheng.

12:20.520 --> 12:22.380
Why is he following you?

12:24.920 --> 12:26.780
No idea. What happened?

12:28.160 --> 12:30.880
What happened indeed?

12:30.880 --> 12:33.120
He told you "I love you".

12:33.120 --> 12:35.292
Stop making fun of me or I'll lose it.

12:35.880 --> 12:37.760
You can't be a dubbing actress.

12:37.760 --> 12:39.964
You blush too easily.

12:40.520 --> 12:43.319
Examine your posts
for anything inappropriate.

12:43.319 --> 12:45.699
Let's leave a good impression.

12:46.240 --> 12:47.199
There's nothing.

12:47.199 --> 12:48.240
Just some complaints.

12:48.240 --> 12:49.959
I post mainly about what to eat

12:49.959 --> 12:51.959
today, tomorrow, or eventually.

12:51.959 --> 12:53.660
Keep looking.

12:55.040 --> 12:56.760
Alright, first things first.

12:56.760 --> 12:58.579
How do I apply for verification?

12:59.199 --> 13:02.679
(ID verification, Requirements)
Click on the page for verification.

13:02.679 --> 13:04.179
Fill in the information.

13:08.450 --> 13:09.880
(Invite 3-6 friends)

13:09.880 --> 13:12.479
It needs verification from my friends?

13:12.479 --> 13:16.120
Yeah, get some verified members
to verify for you.

13:16.120 --> 13:18.972
How many do I need?
I don't have many friends like that.

13:19.640 --> 13:22.040
I think three is enough.

13:22.040 --> 13:24.420
The system will send you
recommendations.

13:25.036 --> 13:25.608
(Invite friends)

13:25.608 --> 13:27.836
(Xiao'an, Perfect Voice_Qiang Qingci)

13:29.199 --> 13:30.620
Perfect.

13:31.920 --> 13:34.719
Qiang Qingci followed you.

13:34.719 --> 13:36.780
That makes it three.

13:37.479 --> 13:39.000
You can't get verified

13:39.000 --> 13:40.819
without him.

13:42.079 --> 13:44.268
Tick all of them. Submit.

13:44.268 --> 13:46.332
(Angel, Xiao'an, Qiang Qingci, Submit)

13:46.920 --> 13:48.839
Am I being rude?

13:48.839 --> 13:50.359
Is it troublesome?

13:50.359 --> 13:51.679
Not really.

13:51.679 --> 13:53.760
He will receive a private message
from the system.

13:53.760 --> 13:55.199
He only has to click on

13:55.199 --> 13:56.839
the button.

13:56.839 --> 14:01.319
And he took the initiative
to follow you.

14:01.319 --> 14:05.319
I bet he wouldn't mind
verifying for you, right?

14:05.319 --> 14:08.620
Hurry up. Submit it.

14:09.644 --> 14:11.319
(We will notify you
of the result in two work days.)

14:11.319 --> 14:13.120
Alright, I'll ask the girls next door

14:13.120 --> 14:15.432
and see if they want a barbecue.

14:15.432 --> 14:17.520
Tell me if you want to invite someone.

14:17.520 --> 14:20.120
And tell me when you're verified. Bye.

14:20.120 --> 14:21.219
Bye.

14:26.119 --> 14:28.520
(Perfect Voice_Qiang Qingci)
(I didn't expect the first message you sent me)

14:28.520 --> 14:30.420
(would be the verification request.)

14:33.559 --> 14:35.660
(Thank you so much.)

14:37.160 --> 14:38.380
(It's okay.)

14:48.199 --> 14:51.179
(Have you ever tried
curry beef noodle soup, sir?)

14:55.640 --> 14:57.359
(Since you like food, )

14:57.359 --> 14:59.900
(let me repay you with a recipe.)

15:04.000 --> 15:06.699
(Chop the beef into chunks.)

15:07.240 --> 15:10.000
(Wash them well
and boil them to take out the blood.)

15:10.000 --> 15:12.719
(Soak the rice noodles in warm water.)

15:12.719 --> 15:17.280
(Add beef, scallion, ginger,
and bay leaves to the water.)

15:17.280 --> 15:21.559
(Boil the water, remove the blood,
add cooking wine to take out the smell, )

15:21.559 --> 15:24.000
(and keep it stewing on a small fire.)

15:24.000 --> 15:26.199
(Boil with curry powder
for five minutes.)

15:26.199 --> 15:28.839
(Add the rice noodles. And it's ready.)

15:28.839 --> 15:30.800
(Oh, don't forget the coriander.)

15:30.800 --> 15:33.939
(It's really nice. I really like it.)

15:39.000 --> 15:41.140
(I know this recipe by heart.)

15:41.679 --> 15:43.132
(It's true.)

15:44.240 --> 15:45.839
(I wanted to pay you back.)

15:45.839 --> 15:48.620
(I guess I should gather more recipes.)

15:49.479 --> 15:50.740
(Pay me back?)

15:51.280 --> 15:54.000
(Yeah, you helped me get verified.)

15:54.000 --> 15:55.620
(I have to pay you back.)

15:56.160 --> 15:57.660
(You mean it?)

16:01.319 --> 16:02.559
(Of course.)

16:02.559 --> 16:04.260
(Sing for me.)

16:06.120 --> 16:07.579
Sing?

16:12.972 --> 16:15.160
(Hospitalization Department)

16:15.160 --> 16:16.459
(Now?)

16:17.479 --> 16:18.588
(Now?)

16:19.120 --> 16:22.479
(No, not now.)

16:22.479 --> 16:24.520
(I'm just asking if you want me)

16:24.520 --> 16:26.520
(to sing now.)

16:26.520 --> 16:27.740
(Just a second.)

16:32.559 --> 16:34.780
(Alright, now.)

16:41.932 --> 16:42.824
(Room 11111520)

16:42.824 --> 16:44.028
(Password 213)

17:01.440 --> 17:03.119
You can speak.

17:03.119 --> 17:04.780
We're alone here.

17:05.319 --> 17:06.659
I'm back.

17:07.879 --> 17:10.919
Well, I'm going to sing.

17:10.919 --> 17:12.899
Go ahead. I'm used to it.

17:22.240 --> 17:24.180
What should I sing?

17:25.960 --> 17:27.579
What are you good at?

17:28.440 --> 17:29.579
Traditional style?

17:31.280 --> 17:32.500
Yeah.

17:33.879 --> 17:38.000
Then let's try "Better Stay Alive".

17:38.000 --> 17:39.819
Better Stay Alive?

17:40.520 --> 17:42.300
It's an interesting song.

17:47.839 --> 17:49.639
Let me find the backing track.

17:49.639 --> 17:50.659
Okay.

17:52.319 --> 17:53.700
Well...

17:54.440 --> 17:55.720
What?

17:55.720 --> 17:58.000
I'm going to sing something weird.

17:58.000 --> 17:59.440
Don't make a sound. Don't laugh.

17:59.440 --> 18:00.899
What is it?

18:02.319 --> 18:04.379
Better Stay Alive.

18:06.200 --> 18:08.579
You're singing that to your fans?

18:09.159 --> 18:12.059
No, it's for Qiang Qingci.

18:12.800 --> 18:14.760
Since when did you become so close?

18:14.760 --> 18:16.240
Why are you singing for him?

18:16.240 --> 18:18.680
(Qiang Qingci's chat room)
He verified my account.

18:18.680 --> 18:20.060
It's like a payback.

18:20.599 --> 18:22.099
Found the backing track?

18:23.079 --> 18:24.040
Go away.

18:24.040 --> 18:25.119
Just sing.

18:25.119 --> 18:27.420
Go away. You make me shy.

18:27.976 --> 18:29.819
Alright.

18:31.240 --> 18:32.700
Go away.

18:37.000 --> 18:38.659
Here we go.

18:47.480 --> 18:48.960
♪ I run. No hesitation ♪

18:48.960 --> 18:50.240
♪ He's a Kungfu Master ♪

18:50.240 --> 18:51.559
♪ Better stay alive ♪

18:51.559 --> 18:52.960
♪ I love boobs and booze ♪

18:52.960 --> 18:54.200
♪ Whistle like a cool guy ♪

18:54.200 --> 18:55.559
♪ Nothing bothers me ♪

18:55.559 --> 18:56.760
♪ Tomorrow will be better ♪

18:56.760 --> 18:58.720
♪ My life matters more ♪

18:58.720 --> 19:01.040
♪ Make friends or run away ♪

19:01.040 --> 19:03.919
♪ I eat more when I win a fight ♪

19:03.919 --> 19:06.399
♪ Messing around, just punch in the air ♪

19:06.399 --> 19:09.240
♪ Stay around and see what's going on ♪

19:09.240 --> 19:11.720
♪ Smile and bow. Laugh out loud ♪

19:11.720 --> 19:14.359
♪ I bow so low to a Kungfu Master ♪

19:14.359 --> 19:17.040
♪ Why bother flashing our weapons ♪

19:17.040 --> 19:19.159
♪ Dong-qiang. Qiang-dong-qiang ♪

19:19.159 --> 19:24.399
♪ Wear away a rock to be a needle?
But we have needles ♪

19:24.399 --> 19:29.720
♪ Put up with your enemies.
The reinforcement only slacks off ♪

19:29.720 --> 19:31.359
♪ Shameless ♪

19:31.359 --> 19:32.760
♪ Disgraceful ♪

19:32.760 --> 19:35.119
♪ I run. No hesitation ♪

19:35.119 --> 19:36.399
♪ He's a Kungfu Master ♪

19:36.399 --> 19:37.639
♪ Better stay alive ♪

19:37.639 --> 19:40.480
♪ I love boobs and booze ♪

19:40.480 --> 19:41.960
♪ Shameless ♪

19:41.960 --> 19:43.280
♪ Disgraceful ♪

19:43.280 --> 19:45.919
♪ Better stay alive. Nothing bothers me ♪

19:45.919 --> 19:47.240
What's so funny?

19:47.240 --> 19:48.240
♪ Tomorrow will be better ♪

19:48.240 --> 19:53.740
♪ My life matters more ♪

19:59.040 --> 20:00.220
Not bad.

20:03.119 --> 20:07.559
Oh, do you like clams?

20:07.559 --> 20:08.732
Yeah.

20:09.280 --> 20:10.460
Get lost.

20:12.200 --> 20:14.680
Yeah, I do. You too?

20:14.680 --> 20:18.780
Kind of. I like it in a certain way.

20:19.599 --> 20:20.780
Clams?

20:22.040 --> 20:24.636
Ever tried spicy clams
with fermented soya beans?

20:26.000 --> 20:28.879
Yeah, but I rarely have spicy food.

20:28.879 --> 20:31.260
It's to protect my throat.

20:34.000 --> 20:36.599
It's medium spicy and easy to make.

20:36.599 --> 20:39.540
It's just hard to clean the clams.

20:44.359 --> 20:47.159
Soak them in salt water for 30 minutes

20:47.159 --> 20:50.559
to make the clams spit out the sand
and clean them well.

20:50.559 --> 20:52.520
Put them in boiled water
so that they open up.

20:52.520 --> 20:56.639
(I hope I can record this for his fans.)

20:56.639 --> 20:59.240
Prepare two seasonings,
one with soy sauce,

20:59.240 --> 21:02.960
sugar, cooking wine,
white pepper, and broth.

21:02.960 --> 21:04.559
Mix them well.

21:04.559 --> 21:08.159
Add some oil to the frying pan.

21:08.159 --> 21:11.000
Fry the fermented soya beans
and smashed garlic.

21:11.000 --> 21:15.480
Cook the stem of scallion,
red peppers, and shredded ginger.

21:15.480 --> 21:18.639
Add the clams and sauce
and cook on high fire.

21:18.639 --> 21:20.399
Once half the water evaporates,

21:20.399 --> 21:23.059
pour in starch water and keep stirring.

21:23.592 --> 21:27.619
In the end,
add the green leaves of the scallion.

21:33.839 --> 21:34.972
Got it?

21:37.200 --> 21:39.680
Got it. Thanks.

21:39.680 --> 21:44.260
I have to go.
When will you sing for me again?

21:44.872 --> 21:46.200
Again?

21:46.200 --> 21:47.819
This is the only time?

21:51.480 --> 21:54.119
Tell me whenever you're free.

21:54.119 --> 21:55.260
Okay.

21:56.839 --> 21:59.220
Bye.

21:59.720 --> 22:00.940
Bye.

22:12.040 --> 22:13.260
What is she doing?

22:20.200 --> 22:22.240
Have you booked the restaurant?

22:22.240 --> 22:23.819
Yeah.

22:31.079 --> 22:34.740
Where are you with Qiang Qingci now?

22:36.000 --> 22:38.000
You're secretly meeting
in his chat room?

22:38.000 --> 22:39.839
Aren't you scared of his fans?

22:39.839 --> 22:41.879
You met in his private chat room?

22:41.879 --> 22:44.399
I just sang a song for him.

22:44.399 --> 22:46.480
You sang a song for him
in his private chat room?

22:46.480 --> 22:49.280
Yeah, it looks like that.

22:49.280 --> 22:51.859
But it's not like that.

22:52.839 --> 22:54.800
Get up. Get changed.

22:54.800 --> 22:57.200
We finished the tests.
The barbecue matters the most.

22:57.200 --> 23:01.500
Sheng, when did you become so close?

23:02.200 --> 23:04.220
There's nothing between us.

23:05.200 --> 23:07.599
I forgot a parcel. Let me get it. Bye.

23:07.599 --> 23:08.899
Sheng.

23:22.399 --> 23:24.240
Dr. Mo became Chef Mo?

23:24.240 --> 23:27.900
I downed my food with those "clams".

23:28.520 --> 23:29.619
You're welcome.

23:30.480 --> 23:33.639
Mo Qingcheng, the chef slash doctor.

23:33.639 --> 23:34.559
Aren't you busy?

23:34.559 --> 23:37.084
I'm swamped.
The Spring Festival is coming.

23:37.680 --> 23:40.639
Oh, got any plans for the festival?

23:40.639 --> 23:42.579
Stay and work. What else?

23:47.079 --> 23:49.540
Condolence from another single guy.

23:53.319 --> 23:56.000
Zheng, it's for me?

23:56.000 --> 23:58.079
No, I'm checking on this unmarried man.

23:58.079 --> 23:59.319
Alright, go ahead.

23:59.319 --> 23:59.720
Alright.

23:59.720 --> 24:00.159
I'll do rounds.

24:00.159 --> 24:01.200
Okay.

24:01.200 --> 24:02.440
Why are you here?

24:02.440 --> 24:04.188
Aren't you flying soon?

24:04.800 --> 24:08.300
You look miserable alone.
So I brought you some supplies.

24:09.280 --> 24:10.720
Thanks.

24:10.720 --> 24:12.260
Don't mention it.

24:15.359 --> 24:17.000
You always work at the hospital

24:17.000 --> 24:19.772
or the studio
during the Spring Festival.

24:20.328 --> 24:22.500
It's quite sad to think about it.

24:23.079 --> 24:25.960
Isn't that nice? It's fulfilling.

24:25.960 --> 24:27.379
Stop kidding me.

24:28.960 --> 24:30.639
Should I book you a ticket?

24:30.639 --> 24:32.659
Celebrate the Spring Festival with me.

24:33.440 --> 24:36.732
All my nephews and nieces
are old enough to run around. It's fun.

24:37.240 --> 24:40.359
And it's snowing in the Northeast.
It's gorgeous.

24:40.359 --> 24:43.119
I can't leave. Besides, I'm used to it.

24:43.119 --> 24:45.052
It's nice to be alone.

24:45.672 --> 24:48.808
Think of it as a vacation
for the Spring Festival.

24:48.808 --> 24:51.879
Fine, I know I can't change your mind.

24:51.879 --> 24:54.639
Doudou got you food at the studio.

24:54.639 --> 24:56.599
Cook for yourself
on the Lunar New Year's Eve.

24:56.599 --> 24:58.579
We'll keep you company online.

24:59.200 --> 25:00.079
Okay.

25:00.079 --> 25:02.119
I'm heading to the airport now.

25:02.119 --> 25:04.919
Okay, safe trip. See you around.

25:04.919 --> 25:07.440
Take care.

25:07.440 --> 25:08.859
Send my regards.

25:10.240 --> 25:11.040
Bye.

25:11.040 --> 25:11.599
Take care.

25:11.599 --> 25:12.668
Okay.

25:13.960 --> 25:14.760
Playing chess?

25:14.760 --> 25:15.899
Yeah.

25:16.440 --> 25:17.919
Keep it straight, boss.

25:17.919 --> 25:19.379
(Fortune)
Rest assured.

25:22.159 --> 25:24.720
Uncle, you have a red envelope for me?

25:24.720 --> 25:27.480
Kiddo, it's too early for that.
Get back to work.

25:27.480 --> 25:29.359
Tell Auntie to make some fish.

25:29.359 --> 25:30.200
Alright.

25:30.200 --> 25:31.839
What's for dinner, Uncle?

25:31.839 --> 25:33.399
(Fortune)
Let me show you.

25:33.399 --> 25:34.919
Hurry up.

25:34.919 --> 25:36.260
Coming, Grandpa.

25:37.768 --> 25:38.280
Wait.

25:38.280 --> 25:38.800
Here?

25:38.800 --> 25:41.159
No, it should be on the left.

25:41.159 --> 25:43.240
You're so illiterate.

25:43.240 --> 25:44.639
Oh, fine. Let me see.

25:44.639 --> 25:45.399
Is it okay?

25:45.399 --> 25:47.560
Yeah. Good. The horizontal scroll.

25:47.560 --> 25:48.159
Okay.

25:48.159 --> 25:48.720
Here.

25:48.720 --> 25:51.139
(Star of Fortune shines upon us)
Alright. Press it.

25:51.800 --> 25:53.280
- Okay.
- Good.

25:53.280 --> 25:54.240
Spring Festival.

25:54.240 --> 25:57.619
Star of Fortune shines upon us.
It brings us fortune and happiness.

26:13.639 --> 26:16.960
I wish you a happy Lunar New Year's Eve
from the North.

26:16.960 --> 26:18.108
Happy New Year.

26:18.800 --> 26:21.940
Happy New Year to you too.

26:25.079 --> 26:27.548
Sheng, let's close down early today.

26:28.200 --> 26:30.720
Stop playing on the phone.
Get the flowers in.

26:30.720 --> 26:32.559
Why don't you do it?

26:32.559 --> 26:35.059
I'm busy. Come on. Hurry up.

26:37.868 --> 26:39.204
(Wangjia Supermarket)

26:42.520 --> 26:43.839
It's a hospital. Do your job!

26:43.839 --> 26:44.399
Easy.

26:44.399 --> 26:46.399
Our kid waited
for the doctor till midnight.

26:46.399 --> 26:49.599
Sir, listen to me. You got us wrong.

26:49.599 --> 26:51.440
No more excuses.
"There are too many kids"?

26:51.440 --> 26:52.879
My kid was sick too.

26:52.879 --> 26:54.579
Again?

26:55.839 --> 26:58.720
They're bothering the doctors.

26:58.720 --> 27:00.200
Looks like it.

27:00.200 --> 27:01.440
It happens all the time.

27:01.440 --> 27:03.879
They'll learn to behave
when nobody wants to be a doctor.

27:03.879 --> 27:06.159
Too many kids are getting sick.

27:06.159 --> 27:08.760
You think I won't hit you
because you're a woman?

27:08.760 --> 27:10.599
Get your supervisor here!

27:10.599 --> 27:11.720
Do you hear me?

27:11.720 --> 27:13.839
Please calm down. We can explain.

27:13.839 --> 27:15.520
Please don't fight.

27:15.520 --> 27:16.559
Please don't fight.

27:16.559 --> 27:19.139
Who are you? None of your business.

27:20.440 --> 27:22.300
What's wrong? You scared me.

27:22.824 --> 27:23.400
Security!

27:23.400 --> 27:24.619
Are you okay?

27:25.159 --> 27:25.879
Geez.

27:25.879 --> 27:27.399
Let me help you.

27:27.399 --> 27:30.800
Bring me that small box from the back.

27:30.800 --> 27:32.879
(Wangjia Supermarket)
Please calm down.

27:32.879 --> 27:33.480
Are you okay?

27:33.480 --> 27:35.159
Are you okay?

27:35.159 --> 27:37.960
I'm fine. Take them in. Are you okay?

27:37.960 --> 27:38.536
We're fine.

27:38.536 --> 27:39.720
Let's go.

27:39.720 --> 27:40.908
We deserve an explanation.

27:40.908 --> 27:42.108
(For ambulance only)

27:44.000 --> 27:45.180
Put it here.

27:49.420 --> 27:51.868
(First People's Hospital)

27:55.839 --> 27:58.428
What are you looking at? You know them?

27:59.159 --> 28:02.579
I saw the doctor
who came for the yogurt.

28:03.879 --> 28:06.460
And you read his fortune.

28:07.079 --> 28:09.800
Yeah, he's quite a decent man.

28:09.800 --> 28:11.659
He protected the girls.

28:12.319 --> 28:15.319
I'll give him a discount next time.

28:15.319 --> 28:17.540
Yeah, you'll cover the shortage.

28:33.319 --> 28:34.599
Is Dr. Mo back?

28:34.599 --> 28:37.559
He's in there. Just a second.

28:37.559 --> 28:38.879
Someone was looking for trouble.

28:38.879 --> 28:42.119
He tried to help and got hit.

28:42.119 --> 28:44.839
We're already overwhelmed
during the Spring Festival.

28:44.839 --> 28:46.300
And this on top of that?

28:49.760 --> 28:52.720
You found an ice pack?
I thought I'd bring you one.

28:52.720 --> 28:54.440
Guess I'm too late.

28:54.440 --> 28:56.188
- Dr. Mo.
- Dr. Mo.

28:56.800 --> 28:58.120
It's okay. Sit.

28:58.120 --> 28:59.240
Okay.

28:59.240 --> 29:01.139
They came to say thank you.

29:01.800 --> 29:03.599
Sorry about that.

29:03.599 --> 29:07.460
It's okay. What did they want?

29:08.000 --> 29:10.720
Too many kids
are having fevers these days.

29:10.720 --> 29:13.399
Several kids came
at the same time last night.

29:13.399 --> 29:15.599
She got overwhelmed.

29:15.599 --> 29:17.680
Those parents accused her of being slow

29:17.680 --> 29:20.460
and came to look for trouble today.

29:21.079 --> 29:24.119
Dr. Mo, are you okay?

29:24.119 --> 29:25.119
I'm okay.

29:25.119 --> 29:27.000
Do something. They're worried.

29:27.000 --> 29:28.339
Right.

29:34.200 --> 29:35.839
It's fine now.

29:35.839 --> 29:38.680
Dr. Mo, thank you so much.

29:38.680 --> 29:39.680
Thank you.

29:39.680 --> 29:41.300
Don't mention it.

29:43.960 --> 29:46.680
Don't rush to leave. Have some water.

29:46.680 --> 29:47.208
Rest a bit.

29:47.208 --> 29:48.319
Okay, thanks.

29:48.319 --> 29:50.119
I have things to do.

29:50.119 --> 29:51.000
Okay.

29:51.000 --> 29:53.020
Zhang Lele, come with me.

29:56.720 --> 29:57.899
What?

29:58.440 --> 29:59.359
Should I sit there

29:59.359 --> 30:01.240
and listen to them saying thank you?

30:01.240 --> 30:03.460
What's wrong with that?

30:05.159 --> 30:06.639
We're late for dinner.

30:06.639 --> 30:08.168
The supermarket sells packed meals.

30:08.168 --> 30:10.520
They taste good. My treat.

30:10.520 --> 30:11.820
Let's go.

30:11.820 --> 30:14.268
(Wangjia Supermarket)

30:23.480 --> 30:27.480
Sheng, come and help me in the storage
once you post the notice.

30:27.480 --> 30:28.579
Okay.

30:32.960 --> 30:34.839
(Happy New Year)
What would you like?

30:34.839 --> 30:36.319
Anything will do.

30:36.319 --> 30:37.720
Why are the lights out?

30:37.720 --> 30:39.919
Yeah, why is it dark?

30:39.919 --> 30:41.610
(Wangjia Supermarket)
What's going on?

30:44.359 --> 30:46.980
(10:00 to 18:00 during the festival)
What a shame.

30:49.839 --> 30:51.720
Never mind. Let's go over there.

30:51.720 --> 30:52.860
Let's go.

30:56.680 --> 30:58.000
Let's go.

30:58.000 --> 31:00.339
(Wangjia Supermarket)
Go. Let me lock up.

31:03.280 --> 31:06.119
- Hello, Xiaoxing.
- Go online tonight.

31:06.119 --> 31:08.200
The Perfect Voice
invites us to their event.

31:08.200 --> 31:09.440
What should we do?

31:09.440 --> 31:10.520
Should we prepare a show?

31:10.520 --> 31:12.720
No need.
They want to discuss the pre-release.

31:12.720 --> 31:13.720
You have to be there.

31:13.720 --> 31:15.300
I'll celebrate with my family
and may not make it.

31:15.300 --> 31:16.000
Don't forget it.

31:16.000 --> 31:17.339
Okay, got it.

31:17.879 --> 31:18.940
Bye.

31:21.480 --> 31:22.839
Put on the helmet.

31:22.839 --> 31:23.859
Okay.

31:27.559 --> 31:29.119
See you later.

31:29.119 --> 31:30.419
See you later.

31:38.440 --> 31:40.520
(The sound of firecrackers
marks the beginning of the year.)

31:40.520 --> 31:43.040
(The whole nation welcomes
the new year together.)

31:43.040 --> 31:44.559
(Let's follow the reporter)

31:44.559 --> 31:48.399
(and take a look at the special dinners
on Lunar New Year's Eve.)

31:48.399 --> 31:51.592
Sis, make some fried tomatoes.

31:51.592 --> 31:52.280
Okay.

31:52.280 --> 31:54.200
Aren't these enough for you?

31:54.200 --> 31:56.040
But I want tomatoes.

31:56.040 --> 31:57.359
We're running out of space.

31:57.359 --> 31:58.500
Give it to me.

32:03.000 --> 32:06.559
They closed the supermarket too soon.

32:06.559 --> 32:08.280
You've been busy the whole year.

32:08.280 --> 32:10.760
Why do you feel bad about
some petty money from those meals?

32:10.760 --> 32:12.399
You have no idea.

32:12.399 --> 32:14.879
The doctors
from the hospital across the street

32:14.879 --> 32:17.180
like the meals I make.

32:17.839 --> 32:21.280
Now I have to see
what nice dishes you've been

32:21.280 --> 32:22.960
serving them.

32:22.960 --> 32:25.280
Nice. They look amazing and smell nice.

32:25.280 --> 32:27.399
We can heat them and share them.

32:27.399 --> 32:27.624
Okay.

32:27.624 --> 32:29.200
And there are clams.

32:29.200 --> 32:32.659
Sheng wrote me the recipe.

32:33.639 --> 32:36.440
Sheng, I'm impressed.

32:36.440 --> 32:39.339
What's wrong?

32:40.040 --> 32:42.419
Smells great. So many dishes.

32:44.839 --> 32:46.960
I heard you were writing recipes.

32:46.960 --> 32:49.680
What? Are you learning cooking
from your mom?

32:49.680 --> 32:52.780
Me? Even Peanut

32:53.280 --> 32:55.260
wouldn't eat what I make.

32:56.280 --> 32:59.399
She's never good at cooking.

32:59.399 --> 33:00.599
That won't do.

33:00.599 --> 33:03.559
Who's going to cook
once your parents grow old?

33:03.559 --> 33:06.020
Will you get takeouts for them all day?

33:07.040 --> 33:08.619
Find someone who can cook.

33:09.280 --> 33:11.720
Well, in that case,

33:11.720 --> 33:13.639
Sheng must look for someone
who can cook.

33:13.639 --> 33:15.940
That's the top criterion.

33:19.760 --> 33:21.500
Go ahead. See you.

33:22.079 --> 33:23.520
She's so shy.

33:23.520 --> 33:25.300
She's a grown kid now.

33:26.636 --> 33:29.596
(First People's Hospital)

33:38.119 --> 33:40.839
They're working overtime
and someone came to pick on them.

33:40.839 --> 33:43.740
Take it to the pediatrician
for condolence.

33:44.720 --> 33:47.559
We know each other well.
It's not needed.

33:47.559 --> 33:50.079
It's the Lunar New Year's Eve.

33:50.079 --> 33:51.200
I'm off now.

33:51.200 --> 33:52.200
Take it to them.

33:52.200 --> 33:53.788
Say it's from you.

33:54.319 --> 33:57.500
I'm getting the credit for what you did?

33:58.039 --> 33:59.339
You...

34:02.439 --> 34:03.919
Take care.

34:03.919 --> 34:05.499
Bye.

34:11.839 --> 34:15.700
Wait, I'm off work too.

34:17.919 --> 34:20.839
Sheng, I went to the heating company.

34:20.839 --> 34:23.359
They said it wasn't easy
to add heating to old houses.

34:23.359 --> 34:25.519
So I got you a heater.

34:25.519 --> 34:26.560
Get by with it.

34:26.560 --> 34:27.760
Thank you, big brother.

34:27.760 --> 34:29.240
Thank you.

34:29.240 --> 34:30.959
You boys.

34:30.959 --> 34:32.439
I fixed your window.

34:32.439 --> 34:33.879
It's sealed now.

34:33.879 --> 34:35.879
Your hands won't freeze
when you play the piano now.

34:35.879 --> 34:38.039
Do you like the new paper cut?

34:38.039 --> 34:39.280
Yeah, thank you, fourth brother.

34:39.280 --> 34:40.160
No problem.

34:40.160 --> 34:42.080
I bought you an air heater.

34:42.080 --> 34:44.479
Turn it on if the heater isn't enough.

34:44.479 --> 34:45.200
One is enough.

34:45.200 --> 34:46.839
That's unnecessary.

34:46.839 --> 34:48.680
She feels cold.

34:48.680 --> 34:50.560
It's the same as big brother's.

34:50.560 --> 34:52.959
You should have asked him. It's too hot.

34:52.959 --> 34:56.039
Easy. I like it, third brother.

34:56.039 --> 34:58.240
I like it a lot. Thanks.

34:58.240 --> 34:59.999
Okay, give it to me.

34:59.999 --> 35:00.760
I got this.

35:00.760 --> 35:00.999
Let me.

35:00.999 --> 35:02.479
No need. You don't know where it is.

35:02.479 --> 35:04.039
Sheng, come here.

35:04.039 --> 35:06.039
Check out the diet recipe

35:06.039 --> 35:07.359
I prepared for you.

35:07.359 --> 35:08.240
Sauces included.

35:08.240 --> 35:09.319
You only have to warm it.

35:09.319 --> 35:11.959
No need.
We're right next to the grocery stores.

35:11.959 --> 35:14.720
Yeah, it's unnecessary.

35:14.720 --> 35:17.359
You have to wash those before cooking.

35:17.359 --> 35:20.160
Now, Sheng can watch TV
and have fun with Grandpa.

35:20.160 --> 35:21.879
Or she can play the piano
and write songs, right?

35:21.879 --> 35:22.319
Come on.

35:22.319 --> 35:24.999
Second brother, I love it.

35:24.999 --> 35:26.200
I even put fruits.

35:26.200 --> 35:27.560
It's fine. Big brother.

35:27.560 --> 35:28.919
- Any drinks?
- I got this.

35:28.919 --> 35:29.760
So talkative.

35:29.760 --> 35:31.760
You got a humidifier, huh?

35:31.760 --> 35:33.240
It's just the winter holiday.

35:33.240 --> 35:34.839
Why are they so nervous?

35:34.839 --> 35:36.640
What? You're jealous?

35:36.640 --> 35:38.879
I dare not.

35:38.879 --> 35:40.560
She's our only sister.

35:40.560 --> 35:41.839
I dare not envy her.

35:41.839 --> 35:43.999
She's born lucky.

35:43.999 --> 35:45.379
That's right.

35:46.240 --> 35:47.879
Come on. Help with the chores.

35:47.879 --> 35:50.300
Grandpa, I'm busy too.

35:56.940 --> 35:58.632
(Peaceful and happy. Wishes come true)

35:58.632 --> 35:59.932
(Fortune)

36:01.420 --> 36:03.519
(The Perfect Voice Studio)

36:03.519 --> 36:04.720
Ms. Wang.

36:04.720 --> 36:07.240
Mr. Mo, aren't you going home?

36:07.240 --> 36:09.500
My parents aren't there. I'll be alone.

36:10.088 --> 36:12.160
But nobody is here.

36:12.160 --> 36:14.399
I know. Happy New Year, Ms. Wang.

36:14.399 --> 36:15.680
Happy New Year.

36:15.680 --> 36:18.720
Go ahead, Mr. Mo. I'm leaving now.

36:18.720 --> 36:19.800
Okay, take care.

36:19.800 --> 36:21.060
Okay.

36:57.292 --> 36:58.460
(WeChat Zhou Zheng)

37:00.760 --> 37:01.979
At nine.

37:03.839 --> 37:05.060
Don't let her win.

37:05.600 --> 37:06.664
Pass.

37:06.664 --> 37:07.240
Almost winning.

37:07.240 --> 37:08.419
Show us.

37:09.039 --> 37:10.640
Grandpa, good luck and win.

37:10.640 --> 37:11.240
Coming.

37:11.240 --> 37:12.479
I'll get you to compose a song.

37:12.479 --> 37:13.240
Sit inside.

37:13.240 --> 37:13.800
Coming.

37:13.800 --> 37:14.560
In the upcoming year,

37:14.560 --> 37:16.959
we should focus on romantic lives

37:16.959 --> 37:18.600
and careers.

37:18.600 --> 37:20.359
Why are you telling Sheng
to get a romantic life?

37:20.359 --> 37:21.439
Got a problem?

37:21.439 --> 37:24.640
Wait. Where did you read that?

37:24.640 --> 37:26.039
From online.

37:26.039 --> 37:28.640
Online? You're seeing someone online.

37:28.640 --> 37:29.384
Online relationship.

37:29.384 --> 37:29.959
Nonsense.

37:29.959 --> 37:30.760
Online relationship.

37:30.760 --> 37:31.600
I...

37:31.600 --> 37:33.099
(It's almost nine. Where are you?)
I don't have time for that.

37:33.099 --> 37:33.600
It's nine.

37:33.600 --> 37:35.164
I'll be in my room.

37:35.800 --> 37:36.640
Sheng is going upstairs.

37:36.640 --> 37:37.519
Give her some food.

37:37.519 --> 37:38.359
Yeah, take some.

37:38.359 --> 37:41.479
No need. Too much. That's enough.

37:41.479 --> 37:43.720
Pork jerky. Duck neck.

37:43.720 --> 37:44.800
Wait.

37:44.800 --> 37:46.039
You gave her so many snacks.

37:46.039 --> 37:48.540
She's going to be thirsty. Take it.

37:49.064 --> 37:50.720
Thanks. See you later.

37:50.720 --> 37:51.240
Alright.

37:51.240 --> 37:52.252
Hold on.

37:52.760 --> 37:55.800
You swear you're not
dating someone, fourth brother?

37:55.800 --> 37:57.680
Come on, don't be so gossipy.

37:57.680 --> 38:00.959
See you. I'll be upstairs. Have fun.

38:00.959 --> 38:01.919
I'll be upstairs.

38:01.919 --> 38:03.339
So many snacks.

38:10.479 --> 38:12.136
Shengshengman is here.

38:12.136 --> 38:13.852
(Happy New Year, Mr. Qiang)

38:18.344 --> 38:19.272
(Shengshengman is the admin?)

38:19.272 --> 38:21.364
(No prying. Focus on the works
Calling Shengshengman)

38:21.388 --> 38:25.308
(Admin: Shengshengman)

38:26.680 --> 38:29.300
(1 message from Qiang Qingci)
(When did I become an admin?)

38:30.039 --> 38:33.339
(We made you a temporary admin
just to make things easier.)

38:36.240 --> 38:38.740
(Okay, thanks.)

38:39.479 --> 38:42.660
(Enter the admin's room.
We're talking about a song recording.)

38:43.596 --> 38:45.319
(Admin group of the Perfect Voice)

38:45.319 --> 38:47.999
(Wang Ke)
As the leader of the Perfect Voice,

38:47.999 --> 38:51.760
I suggest we come up with a pre-release

38:51.760 --> 38:53.720
as a gift for the fans.

38:53.720 --> 38:55.399
Then we'll release

38:55.399 --> 38:58.240
the official song
as a formal gift on the anniversary.

38:58.240 --> 38:59.919
Good idea.

38:59.919 --> 39:02.600
We can take our time
and work on the formal song.

39:02.600 --> 39:05.640
The pre-release can be easy.

39:05.640 --> 39:07.800
Let's find something we all like.

39:07.800 --> 39:10.680
You're a senior member. I'm the leader.
But neither of us have a say.

39:10.680 --> 39:14.620
It's been three years.
Our protagonist is Qiang Qingci.

39:17.879 --> 39:18.899
Sheng.

39:23.280 --> 39:24.379
I'm here.

39:27.080 --> 39:29.560
I remember you like
the traditional Chinese style.

39:29.560 --> 39:30.519
Yeah.

39:30.519 --> 39:32.019
What's your favorite song?

39:33.319 --> 39:35.600
Golden Age.

39:35.600 --> 39:36.924
Golden Age?

39:39.600 --> 39:41.260
That's it then.

39:42.519 --> 39:43.800
Fine by me.

39:43.800 --> 39:45.240
It's quite known.

39:45.240 --> 39:46.879
And it needs many singers.

39:46.879 --> 39:50.959
We need six singers and one narrator.

39:50.959 --> 39:53.120
We're the Perfect Voice.

39:53.120 --> 39:55.839
I say we present it
with the best casting.

39:55.839 --> 39:57.240
So many singers? So sudden?

39:57.240 --> 39:58.319
And the best casting?

39:58.319 --> 40:00.999
It's the festival.
How do we even invite them?

40:00.999 --> 40:05.080
Sheng, who do you have in mind?

40:05.080 --> 40:06.339
Me?

40:08.039 --> 40:12.499
Who would you invite
if you were the producer?

40:14.160 --> 40:17.919
Feishao, Linglong, Momo'er,

40:17.919 --> 40:21.060
Wang Ke, Beidou, Jianjian.

40:22.560 --> 40:26.859
And you have to be the narrator.

40:28.120 --> 40:29.260
Me?

40:33.319 --> 40:37.416
That's easy.
But the singers you mentioned...

40:37.416 --> 40:39.760
They are quite senior in this circle.

40:39.760 --> 40:42.200
Many only hold concerts
and don't sing new songs.

40:42.200 --> 40:45.359
Some don't even hold concerts.

40:45.359 --> 40:47.080
They're just gone

40:47.080 --> 40:50.519
and become legends.

40:50.519 --> 40:53.439
For example, Momo'er.

40:53.439 --> 40:54.819
Momo'er.

40:57.039 --> 40:59.368
What do you think, Doudoubing?

40:59.368 --> 41:01.212
(Welcome home)

41:03.439 --> 41:07.039
Alright, Sheng. I'm flattered.

41:07.039 --> 41:08.540
I'm Momo'er.

41:09.120 --> 41:11.859
Very surprising, huh?

41:13.919 --> 41:17.240
Doudou, you're Momo'er?

41:17.240 --> 41:18.539
That's me.

41:20.359 --> 41:22.600
But you've been gone for ages.

41:22.600 --> 41:25.720
I never knew that you'd be hiding
in the Perfect Voice Studio.

41:25.720 --> 41:27.048
(Feng Yasong)
Surprise, huh?

41:27.048 --> 41:29.479
Doudou has two major accounts.

41:29.479 --> 41:31.640
You're praising me? That's rare.

41:31.640 --> 41:33.680
I'm just stating the fact.

41:33.680 --> 41:35.319
Let's see if the others

41:35.319 --> 41:39.180
will join us for the sake of Mr. Qiang.

41:40.120 --> 41:41.560
Okay, I'll ask them.

41:41.560 --> 41:42.600
But...

41:42.600 --> 41:46.359
But if I remember it right,

41:46.359 --> 41:47.359
Linglong is

41:47.359 --> 41:50.060
a hardcore fan of Qiang Qingci.

41:50.760 --> 41:53.399
A hardcore fan. Sheng, think it through.

41:53.399 --> 41:55.580
Will you give up Qiang Qingci to her?

41:57.519 --> 42:02.060
We don't need her.
Let Shengshengman sing that part.

42:06.919 --> 42:10.200
Sheng, you'll go viral.

42:10.200 --> 42:12.060
No, I can't.

42:13.280 --> 42:15.519
Have some faith in yourself.

42:15.519 --> 42:17.720
We're not on the same level.

42:17.720 --> 42:19.600
They're seniors. I'm a newbie.

42:19.600 --> 42:21.359
And I work behind the screen.

42:21.359 --> 42:24.959
I can compose and write lyrics.
But singing...

42:24.959 --> 42:26.419
You got this.

42:28.160 --> 42:31.339
It's not about popularity.
It's about capability.

42:31.839 --> 42:34.999
Yeah, hasn't everyone
started from the ground up?

42:34.999 --> 42:37.999
Try it. It's just a pre-release anyway.

42:37.999 --> 42:39.560
It's a gift for the fans.

42:39.560 --> 42:41.060
Take it easy.

42:46.600 --> 42:49.019
Okay, I'll try it.

42:49.800 --> 42:52.560
They're my favorite singers.

42:52.560 --> 42:55.439
I never even dreamed of
working with them.

42:55.439 --> 42:57.260
I'll give it my all.

43:18.700 --> 43:24.322
♪ We haven't met before that year ♪

43:25.996 --> 43:32.205
♪ Staring into the starry night ♪

43:33.330 --> 43:39.904
♪ We wonder who we'll
spend our lives with ♪

43:40.626 --> 43:46.464
♪ My thoughts constitute a dream ♪

43:56.946 --> 44:02.598
♪ We just met that year ♪

44:04.172 --> 44:10.016
♪ Fate brought us closer ♪

44:11.506 --> 44:18.349
♪ Our paths are meant to cross ♪

44:18.642 --> 44:24.817
♪ In those years of youth and beauty ♪

44:25.650 --> 44:32.695
♪ When we suddenly turned around ♪

44:33.234 --> 44:40.513
♪ Geese were flying back home ♪

44:46.069 --> 44:51.943
♪ The moment I meet you ♪

44:53.068 --> 44:59.624
♪ I know you're the one I want ♪

45:00.555 --> 45:07.264
♪ No need to prove our love in a hurry ♪

45:07.986 --> 45:15.986
♪ Because it will last forever ♪
